    "In addition, primary stakeholders, could be users or non-users, were the direct recipients of the benefits and risks of AI-enabled systems.",
    "We believed that this learning was valuable and a critical part of RAI practices, thus, as a result, we identified and categorised the stakeholders involved in each included article into these roles: user, non-user, and primary stakeholders.In summary, we extracted the following information from the 45 included articles systematically: title and citation, author(s), publication year, geographical location of data collection or study, study goal, setting (e.g., an industry, 1 3systems were used (46.67%) (Fig. 4).",
